text: George@Hullo, a'm George, sorry fur the wait, ma meeting ran iver. Gin ye'd like tae tak a seat wi kin get sterted.
George@Seo wi received yer aipplication an ye tick aw the boaxes, in terms o qualifications.
George@Wi wanted tae bring ye in tae hae a blether, tawk aboot the joab, and lairn a bit aboot ye.
George@Hoo dies that soond?
Aye, soonds guid.
Yeah, sounds good.
George@Okay.
George@Great.
George@CompanyName haes a roarie history, iz a've nae doot yer aware o! Wance a wee, humble shoe shoap in Glesga, this company has built an empire in selling shoes aroon the warld.
George@A am prood tae wark here, gin ye end up warking here a howp ye dae tae.
A howp sae tae!
I hope so too!
George@Ur ye fa Glesga?
A stay here, bit a'm fae Kilmaurnock.
I live here, but I'm from Kilmarnock.
George@Ha! "Say aye to a killie pie"!
George@It's a guid slogan.
George@Niver tried wan masel.
George@Iz fur the joab itsel, wis there onie questions ye hud? Dae ye want uz tae gi iver the details?
Aye
Yeah
George@Folk hink success in business iz innovation, mairket dominance, labour mairket flexibility, yada yada yada.
George@An there's trith tae at.
George@Bit.
George@A successful business is naehing withoot an airmy o accoontants. Ahin the scenes we ur the glue thit hauds it aw the gither.
George@Whit iz business gin no money management?
Aw aye, am a hunner percent wae ye.
Oh yeah, i'm one hundred percent with you.
George@Guid! A'm gled tae hear it.
George@Kin ye believe folk caw this joab borin?
Folk haver.
People talk nonsense.
George@At they dae.
George@Right weel, it's been a pleasure, a'm sorry bit a've goat anither meetin in five meenits.
George@A'm sorry thit we dinnae hae mair time.
George@We'll bi in touch.
Cheers, see ye later.
Cheers, goodbye.
Janet@Hi Glen, it's Janet fae reception, a'm phonin aboot the interview ye hud wi CompanyName earlier.
Janet@A'm sorry tae say thit we've went wae somewan else.
Janet@George wis sayin he gie enjoayed talkin wi ye, bit he didnae hink ye wir quite the richt fit.
Janet@Best o luck! See ye.
Janet@George wiz gie impressed wi ye, we'd like tae offer ye the joab.
